Install Gradel

install latest java
java -version

Download Gradel Zip File
wget https://services.gradle.org/distributions/gradle-3.4.1-bin.zip

Install Gradel

mkdir /opt/gradle
unzip -d /opt/gradle gradle-3.4.1-bin.zip

export PATH=$PATH:/opt/gradle/gradle-3.4.1/bin

gradle -v


how to build Gradel..?

